  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dbb \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d94\u0db1\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dba\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0ddb\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Online medical service for plantation people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga, Minister of Urban Development and Housing, said that an online medical treatment and counseling service will be started from September 1 for the plantation people.",
        "The Minister mentioned that the New Village Development Authority under the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing will launch this service focusing on Badulla and Idalgashinnawatta.",
        "This medical treatment service project is named as O - DOC, and it costs 100 rupees per month per family.",
        "The minister also said that medical and counseling services can be obtained for all members of the family, and the services of more than 150 doctors are available 24 hours a day.",
        "The Minister said this. Urban Development and Housing Minister Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga said this in a discussion held yesterday (16) at the Ministry of Urban Development and Housing in Setsiripaye, Battaramulla with the officials of Estate Housing Division."
      ],
